  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</u></p>\n<p>. Coordinate project (A&amp;A) works.</p>\n<p>. Manage and supervise projects works as well as oversee all workes, sub-contractor and vendors to ensure proper      work execution and good workmanship.</p>\n<p>. Plan and discuss with sub-contractors on project execution including implementation.</p>\n<p>. Coordinate the project work to ensure sucessful completion as well as hand over to clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Requirements</u></p>\n<p>. Diploma in Building / Certicate in Civil &amp; Structural Engineering or related field.</p>\n<p>. Positive and good working attitude, self-motivated and able to work independently.</p>",
